<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <meta name="color-scheme" content="light">
<meta name="supported-color-schemes" content="light">

    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Abril+Fatface&family=Roboto:wght@100;300;400;500;700;900&display=swap');

        *{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            border: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-family: 'Roboto';
        }

        .wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 25px;
        }

        .wrapper__header {
            width: 100%;
            height: 225px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid black;
        }

        .wrapper__header h1 {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .wrapper__header h3 {
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .wrapper__content {
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .wrapper__content p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .wrapper__content div {
            margin-top: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .wrapper__content a {
            list-style: none;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
        }

        .wrapper__content a div {
           width: 250px;
           height: 45px;
           background-color: #89A3C6;
           display: flex;
           justify-content: center;
           align-items: center;
           border-radius: 2px;
           margin-top: 50px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <header class="wrapper__header">
                <h1>
                    ROAL CASES
                </h1>
                <h3>
                    Hola {{name}}! Bienvenido a Roal Cases Shop
                </h3>
        </header>
        <div class="wrapper__content">
            <p>
                Antes de continuar debes confirmar tu correo electronico, proximamente se mostrara un codigo que debes ingresar en la aplicacion. Despues podras acceder a todas las funciones de la app
            </p>
            <p>
                Tu codigo es:
            </p>
            <div>
                <h3>
                    {{code}}
                </h3>
            </div>
            <p>
                Si no te has registrado en https://roalcases.shop ignora este correo electronico. Gracias por tu atencion.
            </p>

            <a href="localhost:8080/verifyEmail">
                <div>
                    Ir a verificacion
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>